      "index": 1,
      "code": "const { Manifold, CrossSection, label } = api;\n\nconst segments = 48;\n\n// King profile — revolve around Z axis (profile Y = height becomes Z after revolve).\n// Profile traces from center-bottom outward, up to top.\n// In 2D profile: X = radius, Y = height (becomes Z after revolve)\nconst profile = [\n  // Tiered base\n  [0, 0], // center bottom\n  [5.5, 0], // base outer bottom\n  [5.5, 0.8], // base outer rim\n  [4.5, 1.5], // step inward\n  [5.0, 2.0], // second tier outer\n  [5.0, 2.8], // second tier top\n  [4.0, 3.5], // base narrows to stem\n\n  // Stem — slender column\n  [3.2, 4.5], // lower stem\n  [2.8, 7.0], // mid stem taper\n  [2.5, 11.0], // upper stem\n  [2.6, 13.0], // slight swell\n\n  // Crown collar — flares outward near top\n  [2.5, 14.5], // below collar\n  [4.0, 16.0], // collar flare outward\n  [4.2, 17.0], // collar top outer\n  [3.8, 17.8], // collar lip\n\n  // Short neck above collar\n  [2.8, 18.5], // neck\n  [3.0, 20.0], // top of neck / base of cross mount\n\n  // Top knob for cross base\n  [2.5, 21.0], // shoulder\n  [2.0, 22.0], // top of body\n  [0, 22.0], // center top\n];\n\nconst bodyCS = CrossSection.ofPolygons([profile]);\nconst body = Manifold.revolve(bodyCS, segments);\n\n// Cross finial — two rectangular bars forming a cross\n// Vertical bar: 1.5 wide, 1.5 deep, 7 tall, centered at top of body at z=22\nconst crossV = Manifold.cube([1.5, 1.5, 7], true).translate([0, 0, 22 + 3.5]);\n// Horizontal bar: 7 wide, 1.5 deep, 1.5 tall, positioned 2 units up the vertical bar\nconst crossH = Manifold.cube([7, 1.5, 1.5], true).translate([0, 0, 22 + 2.5]);\n\nconst cross = crossV.add(crossH);\n\nreturn label(body, 'body').add(label(cross, 'cross'));\n",
